<plot>Mr. Bee spreads the word that there is going to be a 'PM Picnic' in the barn latter that evening. He tells everyone in the countryside, from Mr. Bear to Mr. Rabit, although he does not invite Mr. Tortus because he's too slow. This was a promotional film made for PM (Plesent Moments) Whiskey to promote their new ad campaign, that features animated woodland creatures along with the slogan describing PM Whiskey and it's 'Clear, Clean Taste'.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?419541</url></doc>
